Quote list

Mastering others is strength mastering yourself is true power - Lao Tzu
the only person you are destined to become is the person you decide to be - ralph waldo emerson
Humility is the solid foundation of all virtues - confucius
Good enough equals shitty  – Brian Grazer
Money is like gas during a road trip. You don’t want to run out of gas on your trip, but you’re not doing a tour of gas stations.” – Tim O’Reilly

What were things like before we started working together?
What made them look for a professional or a firm to help them with that problem?
How did they find you?
What were the obstacles to making a decision?
Why did they choose your firm?
Now that we’ve worked together, now that we’ve completed the project, now that the engagement is over, now that we’ve delivered this thing to you, how are things now? What is life like? What is business like?
What are three benefits that they’ve experienced through working with you?
What was your favorite part of the experience working with us?
Would you recommend that others work with us, and if so, why?
Anything else you think is important to mention?